    "data": {
        "description": {
            "value": "<p><strong>Prerequisites</strong> <a class=\"entity-link\" data-pack=\"pf2e.feats-srd\" data-id=\"y7DDs03GtDnmhxFp\" draggable=\"true\"><i class=\"fas fa-suitcase\"></i> Poisoner Dedication</a>, trained in Medicine</p>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong> Your last action was a successful melee <a class=\"entity-link\" data-pack=\"pf2e.actionspf2e\" data-id=\"VjxZFuUXrCU94MWR\" draggable=\"true\"><i class=\"fas fa-suitcase\"></i> Strike</a><br>that dealt damage against a target that is afflicted by a <br>poison, and you know which poison.</p>\n<hr>\n<p>Poisons attack specific parts of the body—one venom might target the lungs, another the circulatory system, while another deteriorates the nerves. You know how to take advantage of such weaknesses.</p>\n<p>You deal <a class=\"inline-roll roll\" data-mode=\"roll\" data-flavor=\"\" data-formula=\"1d6\" title=\"1d6\"><i class=\"fas fa-dice-d20\"></i> 1d6</a> damage of the required Strike’s damage type and <a class=\"inline-roll roll\" data-mode=\"roll\" data-flavor=\"poison\" data-formula=\"1d6\" title=\"poison\"><i class=\"fas fa-dice-d20\"></i> 1d6</a> poison damage to the target. If you’re at least 18th level, you deal <a class=\"inline-roll roll\" data-mode=\"roll\" data-flavor=\"\" data-formula=\"2d6\" title=\"2d6\"><i class=\"fas fa-dice-d20\"></i> 2d6</a> damage of each type.</p>",
